snippet.title: Preview of Honkai Impact 3rd Part 1 Finale Opening - Honkai Impact 3rd
snippet.description:
*Spoiler Alert

The blue planet reflects clear rays far off, as if a giant eyeball staring at us from the distance.
The blue feels intimate and familiar, so familiar that one would almost develop fear upon seeing it.
The planet is going to embrace its destiny, which shall be determined by humanity, not Honkai.
